trans-unit.source: Consists of a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects to be used with catalogs of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: É composta por uma coleção de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref> objetos para ser utilizado com catálogos de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> controlos.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Esta classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection class is created by the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in their implementations of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: A classe de WebPartDescriptionCollection é criada por vários <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>controlos as respetivas implementações do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>método.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: For each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control that is contained in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control, a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object is created.
trans-unit.target: Para cada <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controlo que está contido num <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>controlo, um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objeto é criado.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: This object maintains basic information about a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, including its ID, its title, its description, and a path to an associated icon.
trans-unit.target: Este objeto mantém informações básicas sobre um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controlo, incluindo o respetivo ID, o título, a descrição e um caminho para um ícone associado.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls can use a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to display a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control's information in the catalog, without having to create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control itself.
trans-unit.target: Vários <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>controlos podem utilizar um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objecto a mostrar uma <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>as informações do controlo no catálogo, sem ter de criar uma instância do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>controlar a próprio.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection class is used internally by the Web Parts control set to maintain a collection of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects used in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: A classe de WebPartDescriptionCollection é utilizada internamente pelo controlo definido para manter uma coleção de todas as peças Web a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objetos utilizados no catálogo.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection collection is used only when a page is in catalog display mode.
trans-unit.target: A coleção de WebPartDescriptionCollection é utilizada apenas quando uma página está no modo de visualização de catálogo.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control is being rendered, it loops through the WebPartDescriptionCollection collection, adding the information from each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to the displayed catalog.
trans-unit.target: Quando um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>controlo está a ser composto, repete através da coleção de WebPartDescriptionCollection, adicionar as informações de cada <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objeto para o catálogo apresentado.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an empty new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância vazia do <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: This overload of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A> constructor can be used to create an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Esta sobrecarga do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A>construtor pode ser utilizado para criar uma coleção vazia.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> control creates an empty <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> object if the content of an imported description file is `null`.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>controlo cria vazio <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection>objeto se o conteúdo de um ficheiro de descrição importado é `null`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"></xref> object by passing in an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância de um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"> </xref> objeto mediante a transmissão num <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>coleção de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref> objetos.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection constructor is used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method implementations within the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls to create a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects.
trans-unit.target: O construtor de WebPartDescriptionCollection é utilizado pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>implementações de método dentro várias <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>controlos para criar uma coleção de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objetos.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects that correspond to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls in a catalog.
